===============================================================================
                               CHANGELOG
===============================================================================

[0.5.0] - 2026-07-14
--------------------
Added:
  - PackageManager high-level facade for package management
  - ArchiveTooLarge error variant for package size validation
  - remove_file and metadata methods to FileSystem trait
  - Re-export PackageManager and update public API
  - Required rawssg/files/install fields, edition field, and resolve_target_dir

Changed:
  - FileSystem trait integration throughout: package creation, extraction,
    manifest, lock file, install/remove, fetch
  - Accept FileSystem and return optional extracted directory in extraction
    functions
  - Enforce file type and size checks during package creation/extraction

Documentation:
  - Updated README for v0.5.0 with PackageManager and edition 2024 details

Build & CI:
  - Bump version to 0.5.0
  - Update lockfile
  - Simplify CI workflow: remove clippy and format jobs

Testing:
  - Added comprehensive test suite: PackageManager, verify, types, package ops,
    manifest, lock file, install/remove, filesystem, filter, fetch, checksum,
    MockFs, MockHttp


[0.3.2] - 2026-07-14
--------------------
Added:
  - Required fields (rawssg, files, install) with constructor for configuration
  - Re-export FileSystem and RealFs
  - remove_file method to FileSystem trait and RealFs implementation

Changed:
  - Refactored to accept FileSystem throughout: verify_package, package
    creation/extraction/move, manifest load/save, lock file load/save,
    install_package, remove_package, fetch_package

Documentation:
  - Bump version to 0.3.2 in README

Build & CI:
  - Bump version to 0.3.2
  - Update lockfile


[0.3.1] - 2026-07-14
--------------------
Changed:
  - Bump Rust edition to 2024

Documentation:
  - Update version and edition in README

Build & CI:
  - Bump version to 0.3.1
  - Update lockfile
  - Update GitHub Actions: checkout v7, cache v6


[0.3.0] - 2026-07-14
--------------------
Added:
  - HttpClient trait and UreqClient implementation for HTTP fetching
  - Re-export HttpClient and UreqClient
  - Comprehensive CI workflow

Testing:
  - Added extensive test suite covering: verify, types, package
    creation/extraction, manifest, lock file, install/remove, filesystem,
    filter, fetch, checksum
  - MockFs for unit testing

Documentation:
  - Update version to 0.3.0 in README

Build & CI:
  - Bump version to 0.3.0


[0.2.0] - 2026-07-14
--------------------
Added:
  - Initial library implementation: package management, manifest handling, file
    filtering, checksum generation/verification, abstract filesystem (RealFs),
    package fetching, lock file management, configuration types
  - Package verification, creation, extraction, relocation, installation, removal
  - Error types with miette diagnostics
  - Include/exclude file filtering with glob

Changed:
  - Renamed LibrawdistError to RawdistError, LibrawdistConfig to RawdistConfig
    with load_from_dir method
  - Various refactors for FileSystem injection and error handling
  - Updated dependencies

Fixed:
  - Build errors: fix temp_dir.keep() usage and ureq read_to_vec

Documentation:
  - Comprehensive README with API docs, examples, config reference
  - Added GPL-3.0 license
  - Project status documentation

Build & CI:
  - Added Cargo.toml, Cargo.lock
  - Bump version to 0.2.0
